## Implementation Guide

1. Navigate to Campaigns → Settings → Locations
2. Click "Location options" → "Advanced search"
3. For each location, set bid adjustment:
   - Bid up locations: +20% to +50%
   - Bid down locations: -20% to -50%
   - Excluded locations: Click "Exclude"
4. Monitor for 14 days, adjust as needed

## Expected Results

- ROAS improvement: 15-25%
- Cost efficiency: 10-15% savings from bid downs and exclusions
- Revenue increase: 10-20% from bid ups on top locations

